## Build Script — `generate-troubleshoot-responses.mjs`

Reuse `scripts/utils/gemini-client.mjs` patterns. The script:
1. Globs `docs/**/*.md` for `<Troubleshoot mode="general">` entries (both prop orderings)
2. Loads existing `generated-responses.json`
3. Calls Gemini for any missing/empty keys via `Promise.allSettled`
4. Writes merged results back
5. Always exits 0 so builds continue on failure

Update `package.json` build script:
```
node scripts/generate-troubleshoot-responses.mjs && export NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=10240 && DOCUSAURUS_IGNORE_SSG_WARNINGS=true docusaurus build
```

