## Netlify Function — `kapa_proxy.mts`

Proxies to `https://api.kapa.ai/query/v1/projects/{KAPA_WEBSITE_ID}/chat/` using `X-API-KEY: process.env.KAPA_API_KEY`. Returns `{ answer: string }`. Handles OPTIONS, validates body, logs errors. Website ID: `db287d54-3525-4674-9d83-a0cbe35024d2`.

