## FAQ Component — `FAQ.tsx`

- Default `mode="docs"`. `mode="general"` is not meaningful on FAQ — avoid it.
- `useAIResponse` handles fetching. No toggle/lazy logic in the component.
- Always wrap in `BrowserOnly`.

---

## Troubleshoot Component — `Troubleshoot.tsx`

- Default `mode="general"`.
- `mode="general"`: synchronous JSON lookup from `generated-responses.json` — instant.
- `mode="docs"`: progress bar while fetching, content when done.
- `mode="fallback-only"`: always static.
- Do **not** add `###` headings above entries — `issue` prop is the collapsible heading.

