## Constraints

- Always wrap in `BrowserOnly` — SSR will break without it.
- `fallback` prop is required on every entry. Never omit it.
- `generated-responses.json` is **gitignored**; `generate-troubleshoot-responses.mjs` creates `{}` when missing so imports resolve. CI/production builds with `GEMINI_API_KEY` populate it at build time.
- Do not create `gemini_proxy.mts`. `kapa_proxy.mts` is intentional.
- Do not expose `GEMINI_API_KEY` in client-side code.
- Do not add toggle/lazy-fetch logic to components — `useAIResponse` handles eager fetching.
